{"tid":1741276,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"各行各業籌款支持香港人權運動","createTime":"2019-11-20T09:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T14:47:19.000Z","uid":168469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eee17d11456362178232f805b2eb6afe7dadebe1","tid":1741276,"uid":168469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:14:00.000Z","msg":"目前，香港社會好多人受傷，好多人需要幫助。篩<br />\n為了籌錢幫助有需要的人，同時又比機會每個巿民用自己的長處參與這場運動，<br />\n本組織召募一班支持香港人權運動的義工。<br />\n工作內容很簡單，只是做返自己原來的職業，但係唔收客人錢，只係邀請客人捐錢比<br />\n香港人權運動組織。<br />\n至於哪裡是「香港人權運動組織」，則由義工自行決定，然後向客人說明。<br />\n為了尊重自由和人權，本運動不會對義工指定的「人權組織」作出篩選<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfxGAdGzM56AVs2XGhNCQLcEZDGPR4GWR6eYQW-FKB8Th6ggg/viewform?fbclid=IwAR2hKwB5qMrFNEbp2Y6cVLpieAyhbKi-AoAPeTLHvlj-6A3RvmPBvI4UsNU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfxGAdGzM56AVs2XGhNCQLcEZDGPR4GWR6eYQW-FKB8Th6ggg%2Fviewform%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2hKwB5qMrFNEbp2Y6cVLpieAyhbKi-AoAPeTLHvlj-6A3RvmPBvI4UsNU&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLCWHaP8IcnP89ZPrefCyuoo%3D&h=c2caedf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfxGAdGzM56AVs2XGhNCQLcEZDGPR4GWR6eYQW-FKB8Th6ggg/viewform?fbclid=IwAR2hKwB5qMrFNEbp2Y6cVLpieAyhbKi-AoAPeTLHvlj-6A3RvmPBvI4UsNU</a>"},{"pid":"64289a008d43248d5c21126207b44bc6c68135b0","tid":1741276,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T13:43:44.000Z","msg":"又黎無國界"},{"pid":"65e0a89d638a2257a0ae08927732c5ad97bb7491","tid":1741276,"uid":168469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64289a008d43248d5c21126207b44bc6c68135b0","tid":1741276,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T13:43:44.000Z","msg":"又黎無國界"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:47:19.000Z","msg":"為了尊重自由和人權，本運動不會對義工指定的「人權組織」作出篩選"}]}